==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unsecret
<hw>Un*se"cret</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>secret</ets>.]</ety> <def>To disclose; to
divulge.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsecret</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unsecret
<hw>Un*se"cret</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> not +
<ets>secret</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not secret; not close; not trusty;
indiscreet.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧We are <xex>unsecret</xex>
to ourselves.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsecularize</ent>⟦br⟧
